text.__SUMMARY__: Ondina normani is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Pyramidellidae, the pyrams and their allies.
text.Distribution:
This species occurs in the following locations:
European waters (ERMS scope)
Arctic Seas
United Kingdom Exclusive Economic Zone
